### Verum Omnis API Smoke Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@host = gitverum.web.app

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Health Check (Production)
GET https://{{host}}/api/health

###

### V1 Verify (Health Check)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/verify

###

### Chat Endpoint - Valid Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello, test message"
}

###

### Chat Endpoint - Missing Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

